title: How to Paint: Shadowy Green Armour
description:
The Van Saar are a Necromundan House of great technical expertise, known for bringing a striking armoured style to underhive battles. In this guide, we’ll show you how to paint shadowy green armour on the Van Saar Arachni-rig – but you can use this Warhammer Painting guide for any models in your collection.        

If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it
